Homework assignment #11
. Please include you first name as part of the program file name
. Email your program to teacher. Due 03/15/2017 9pm. 

Banking
Assume you have a bank account with initial balance 0. Program a banking system that keeps asking you for three options:
1. Deposit. Then ask user to input the amount of money to deposit and update the balance.
2. Withdraw. Then ask user to input the amount of money to withdraw and update the balance.
3. Exit. Finish the program.

Requirements:
1. Use a global variable to keep track of the balance.
2. To update balance, define different functions for deposit and withdraw
3. Also define a function to print out the current balance
4. For withdrawing, if the available balance is less than the requsted money, then only withdraw the available balance
